Rules For Imperative
ना / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Neutral)] / X
Null / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Intimate)]/ X
// All Verbs
// Null / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,imperative] / Vc or Ve or Vii
 ो  / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Semi-honorific)] / VC or Ve
ओ  / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Semi-honorific)] / Vaa or Vii or Vuu or Vo or caus or trans
जिए  / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Honorific)] / Vii or Ve
ए  / [x,x,x,x,x,x,x,(Imperative : Honorific)]/ Vaa or Vo or Vuu or VC or caus or trans
इए  / [+imperative,+polite] / Vx

Rules For Conjunctive
कर  / [x,x,x,(Past, Conjunctive), Participle,x]

Rules For Perfective
आ  / [masc,sg,x,x,perfect,x] / Vuu or Vo
ा   / [masc,sg,x,x,perfect,x] / VC
 े / [masc,pl,x,x,perfect,x] / VC
 ी  / [fem,sg,x,x,perfect,x] / VC
 ीं  / [fem,pl,x,x,perfect,x] / VC
या  / [masc,sg,x,x,perfect,x] / Vaa or Vo or Ve or Vii or caus or trans
//(including caus and trans)
ए or ये  / [masc,pl,x,x,perfect,x] / Vaa or Vo or Ve or Vii or caus or trans
//(including caus and trans)
//एँ or एं or यें  / [masc,pl,x,x,perfect,x] / Vaa or Vo or Ve or Vii or caus or trans
//(including caus and trans)
ई or यी   / [fem,pl,x,x,perfect,x]/ Vaa or Vo or Ve or Vii or caus or trans
//(including caus and trans)
ईं or यीं / [fem,pl,x,x,perfect,x]/ Vaa or Vo or Ve or Vii or caus or trans
//(including caus and trans)

Rules For AGR2
//(gender-number) after ग, त, न and other auxiliaries
ा   / [masc,sg,x,x,x,x]
  े / [masc,pl,x,,x,x,x]
 ी   / [fem,sg/pl,x,x,x,x]
 ीं  / [fem,pl,x,x,x,x]

